sections.heading: National Uniform Standards of Professional Appraisal Practice Course, defined
sections.text: Fifteen-hour National Uniform Standards of Professional Appraisal Practice Course means the course as approved by the Appraiser Qualifications Board.SourceLaws 2014, LB717, ยง 7;R.S.Supp.,2014, ยง 76-2212.01;Laws 2015, LB139
